{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Today, I want you to look at"},{"time":3000,"text":"children who become suicide bombers"},{"time":6000,"text":"through a completely different lens."},{"time":8000,"text":"In 2009, there were 500"},{"time":11000,"text":"bomb blasts across Pakistan."},{"time":13000,"text":"I spent the year working"},{"time":15000,"text":"with children"},{"time":17000,"text":"who were training to become suicide bombers"},{"time":19000,"text":"and with Taliban recruiters,"},{"time":21000,"text":"trying to understand how the Taliban"},{"time":23000,"text":"were converting these children"},{"time":25000,"text":"into live ammunition"},{"time":27000,"text":"and why these children were actively"},{"time":29000,"text":"signing up to their cause."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"I want you to watch a short video"},{"time":33000,"text":"from my latest documentary film, \"Children of the Taliban.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"(Singing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":43000,"text":"The Taliban now run their own schools."},{"time":48000,"text":"They target poor families"},{"time":50000,"text":"and convince the parents to send their children."},{"time":53000,"text":"In return, they provide free food and shelter"},{"time":56000,"text":"and sometimes pay the families a monthly stipend."},{"time":61000,"text":"We've obtained a propaganda video"},{"time":63000,"text":"made by the Taliban."},{"time":66000,"text":"Young boys are taught justifications"},{"time":69000,"text":"for suicide attacks"},{"time":71000,"text":"and the execution of spies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75000,"text":"I made contact with a child from Swat"},{"time":77000,"text":"who studied in a madrassa like this."},{"time":81000,"text":"Hazrat Ali is from a"},{"time":83000,"text":"poor farming family in Swat."},{"time":85000,"text":"He joined the Taliban a year ago"},{"time":87000,"text":"when he was 13."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91000,"text":"How do the Taliban in your area get people to join them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":96000,"text":"Hazrat Ali: They first call us to the mosque and preach to us."},{"time":100000,"text":"Then they take us to a madrassa"},{"time":103000,"text":"and teach us things from the Koran."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"Sharmeen Obaid Chinoy: He tells me that children"},{"time":108000,"text":"are then given months of military training."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111000,"text":"HA: They teach us to use machine guns, Kalashnikov,"},{"time":116000,"text":"rocket launchers, grenades, bombs."},{"time":119000,"text":"They ask us to use them only against the infidels."},{"time":125000,"text":"Then they teach us to do a suicide attack."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129000,"text":"SOC: Would you like to carry out a suicide attack?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":131000,"text":"HA: If God gives me strength."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137000,"text":"SOC: I, in my research,"},{"time":139000,"text":"have seen that the Taliban have perfected"},{"time":141000,"text":"the way in which they recruit"},{"time":143000,"text":"and train children,"},{"time":145000,"text":"and I think it's a five-step process."},{"time":148000,"text":"Step one is that the Taliban prey"},{"time":150000,"text":"on families that are large, that are poor,"},{"time":153000,"text":"that live in rural areas."},{"time":155000,"text":"They separate the parents from the children"},{"time":157000,"text":"by promising to provide food, clothing,"},{"time":159000,"text":"shelter to these children."},{"time":161000,"text":"Then they ship them off, hundreds of miles away"},{"time":164000,"text":"to hard-line schools"},{"time":166000,"text":"that run along the Taliban agenda."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168000,"text":"Step two:"},{"time":170000,"text":"They teach the children the Koran, which is Islam's holiest book,"},{"time":173000,"text":"in Arabic, a language these children do not understand"},{"time":176000,"text":"and cannot speak."},{"time":178000,"text":"They rely very heavily on teachers,"},{"time":181000,"text":"who I have personally seen"},{"time":183000,"text":"distort the message to these children"},{"time":185000,"text":"as and when it suits their purpose to."},{"time":188000,"text":"These children are explicitly forbidden"},{"time":190000,"text":"from reading newspapers, listening to radio,"},{"time":193000,"text":"reading any books"},{"time":195000,"text":"that the teachers do not prescribe them."},{"time":197000,"text":"If any child is found violating these rules,"},{"time":200000,"text":"he is severely reprimanded."},{"time":203000,"text":"Effectively, the Taliban create"},{"time":205000,"text":"a complete blackout"},{"time":207000,"text":"of any other source of information for these children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"Step three: The Taliban want these children"},{"time":213000,"text":"to hate the world that they currently live in."},{"time":216000,"text":"So they beat these children --"},{"time":218000,"text":"I have seen it;"},{"time":220000,"text":"they feed them twice a day dried bread and water;"},{"time":223000,"text":"they rarely allow them to play games;"},{"time":226000,"text":"they tell them that, for eight hours at a time,"},{"time":228000,"text":"all they have to do is read the Koran."},{"time":231000,"text":"The children are virtual prisoners;"},{"time":233000,"text":"they cannot leave, they cannot go home."},{"time":236000,"text":"Their parents are so poor,"},{"time":238000,"text":"they have no resources to get them back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240000,"text":"Step four: The older members of the Taliban,"},{"time":243000,"text":"the fighters,"},{"time":245000,"text":"start talking to the younger boys"},{"time":247000,"text":"about the glories of martyrdom."},{"time":249000,"text":"They talk to them about how when they die,"},{"time":252000,"text":"they will be received up"},{"time":255000,"text":"with lakes of honey and milk,"},{"time":257000,"text":"how there will be 72 virgins"},{"time":259000,"text":"waiting for them in paradise,"},{"time":261000,"text":"how there will be unlimited food,"},{"time":264000,"text":"and how this glory"},{"time":266000,"text":"is going to propel them to become"},{"time":268000,"text":"heroes in their neighborhoods."},{"time":271000,"text":"Effectively, this is the brainwashing process"},{"time":274000,"text":"that has begun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276000,"text":"Step five: I believe the Taliban have"},{"time":278000,"text":"one of the most effective"},{"time":280000,"text":"means of propaganda."},{"time":283000,"text":"Their videos that they use"},{"time":285000,"text":"are intercut with photographs"},{"time":288000,"text":"of men and women and children"},{"time":290000,"text":"dying in Iraq and Afghanistan"},{"time":292000,"text":"and in Pakistan."},{"time":294000,"text":"And the basic message is that the Western powers"},{"time":296000,"text":"do not care about civilian deaths,"},{"time":298000,"text":"so those people who live"},{"time":300000,"text":"in areas and support governments"},{"time":302000,"text":"that work with Western powers are fair game."},{"time":305000,"text":"That's why Pakistani civilians,"},{"time":307000,"text":"over 6,000 of whom have been killed in the last two years alone,"},{"time":310000,"text":"are fair game."},{"time":312000,"text":"Now these children are primed"},{"time":314000,"text":"to become suicide bombers."},{"time":316000,"text":"They're ready to go out and fight"},{"time":318000,"text":"because they've been told that this is"},{"time":320000,"text":"effectively their only way"},{"time":322000,"text":"to glorify Islam."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324000,"text":"I want you to watch another excerpt from the film."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330000,"text":"This boy is called Zenola."},{"time":332000,"text":"He blew himself up, killing six."},{"time":337000,"text":"This boy is called Sadik."},{"time":339000,"text":"He killed 22."},{"time":344000,"text":"This boy is called Messoud."},{"time":347000,"text":"He killed 28."},{"time":352000,"text":"The Taliban are running suicide schools,"},{"time":355000,"text":"preparing a generation of boys"},{"time":357000,"text":"for atrocities against civilians."}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"Do you want to carry out a suicide attack?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":364000,"text":"Boy: I would love to."},{"time":367000,"text":"But only if I get permission from my dad."},{"time":372000,"text":"When I look at suicide bombers younger than me, or my age,"},{"time":379000,"text":"I get so inspired by their terrific attacks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383000,"text":"SOC: What blessing would you get"},{"time":385000,"text":"from carrying out a suicide attack?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":388000,"text":"Boy: On the day of judgment, God will ask me,"},{"time":391000,"text":"\"Why did you do that?\""},{"time":396000,"text":"I will answer, \"My Lord! Only to make you happy!"},{"time":402000,"text":"I have laid down my life fighting the infidels.\""},{"time":409000,"text":"Then God will look at my intention."},{"time":416000,"text":"If my intention was to eradicate evil for Islam,"},{"time":424000,"text":"then I will be rewarded with paradise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430000,"text":"Singer: ♫ On the day of judgment ♫"},{"time":434000,"text":"♫ My God will call me ♫"},{"time":436000,"text":"♫ My body will be put back together ♫"},{"time":440000,"text":"♫ And God will ask me why I did this ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":445000,"text":"SOC: I leave you all with this thought:"},{"time":448000,"text":"If you grew up in these circumstances,"},{"time":451000,"text":"faced with these choices,"},{"time":453000,"text":"would you choose to live in this world"},{"time":456000,"text":"or in the glorious afterlife?"},{"time":458000,"text":"As one Taliban recruiter told me,"},{"time":461000,"text":"\"There will always be sacrificial lambs in this war.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":464000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":466000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}